From food to toiletries to household goods, cosmetics and much more, The Agha’s Supermarket is a one-stop-shop for all your daily needs and those little treats that make your day special. So just take your trolley and fill up on the good things in life. \n\nGourmet cheese, exotic chocolates, aisles full of all kinds of delicacies- that’s Agha’s Supermarket. Karachi’s leading retail giant, Agha’s Supermarket is a world of indulgence and day-to-day delights.
